com.saxonica.schema
Interface Term

All Known Implementing Classes:
AllCompositor, ChoiceCompositor, Compositor, ElementDecl, ElementWildcard, ModelGroupDefinition, SequenceCompositor
public interface Term

Represents a Term in a content model as defined by XML Schema. The term may be an element declaration, a wildcard, a sequence, a choice, or all. Terms are not schema components in their own right. Essentially a Particle is a Term together with a maxOccurs and minOccurs. Therefore, terms do not have their own properties, which is why Term here is just a marker interface.
